	('z0oLSlN', '902d8da5-9b73-47fe-be52-db8d9af27ae6', 'The concept of the "best" mean is subjective and depends on the specific context or what is being measured. In statistics, there are various measures of central tendency, including the arithmetic mean, median, and mode. 

